MIT License

This project ("webForecast") packages the "timesfm-from-scratch" model by
Fareed Khan for zero-server, client-side WebGPU inference in the browser.

  Model architecture, training code, and the 70M checkpoint:
    Copyright (c) 2026 Fareed Khan
    https://github.com/FareedKhan-dev/timesfm-from-scratch
    https://huggingface.co/FareedKhan/timesfm-from-scratch-70m
    (model/layers.py, model/revin.py, model/timesfm.py are vendored from that
     repository, which is MIT-licensed; this notice is retained per its terms.)

  Browser deployment, ONNX export tooling, sample datasets, and web app:
    Copyright (c) 2026 Vishal Mysore
    https://github.com/vishalmysore/webForecast

